languages.text: "Хорошее место. Похоже на грузовую магистраль флагмана. Почти дом".
languages.translation_comment: Argenta: "The Shadow Quarters... When I was last on Footfall, I used to take my weapon and wander this area, anticipating an encounter with a mutant or a bandit."

languages.text: "I enjoy it here. This place reminds me of the flagship's freight line. Almost like home."
